To run chatserve.py

Give it executable permissions: chmod +x chatserve.py

Run by using the command python chatserve.py <server_port>


To run the client side chatclient.cpp

To Compile use the following: gcc chatclient.cpp -o chatClient

Run by using the command: chatclient <server_ip> <server_port>

I tested this program on flip2.engr.oregonstate.edu

The first message must be sent on chatclient.